   <text>
      <body>
         <div type="translation">
            <ab>"Receipt of me, Phoibammon presbyter. I have received from Anup and Lemesas as a loan twenty-eight artabas of wheat and (I acknowledge that) I shall deliver them to you on the threshing-floor in the D. V. third indiktion, total 28 art. of wheat only. Through me, Phoibammon presbyter, I agree. Phaophi 30 of the 2nd indiktion."</ab>
         </div>
